gurmukhi: pwgVdI pvMg ] swgVdI suBMg ] jwgVdI juAwx ] JwgVdI JuJwx ]14]170]
transliteration: Paagaddoo Pavan|| Saagaddoo Soubhan|| Jaagaddoo Juaan|| Jhaagaddoo Jhujhaan||14||170||
translation: The winsome brave horse-riders were fighting courageously.14.170.

gurmukhi: JwgVdI JVMg ] kwgVdI kVMg ] qwgVdI qVwk ] cwgVdI ctwk ]15]171]
transliteration: Jhaagaddoo Jhadan|| Kaagaddoo Kadan|| Taagaddoo Tadaak|| Chaagaddoo Chataak||15||171||
translation: Several types of noise were spreading in the battlefield.15.171.
The arms were being swung in the battlefield and the stream of blood was flowing.
Manifesting her frightful form, Kapali Durga was dancing.16.172.

gurmukhi: AnMq dust mwrIXM ] ibAMq sok twrIXM ]
transliteration: Anant Doust Marooyan|| Biant Sok Tdarooyan||
translation: Killing the countless tyrants, Durga effaced many sufferings.

gurmukhi: kmMD AMD au`TIXM ] ibsyK bwx bu`TIXM ]17]173]
transliteration: Kamanndh Andh Outthooyan|| Bisekh Baan Boutthooyan||17||173||
translation: The blinds trunks were rising and moving and they were being felled on the ground with the shower of arrows.17.173.

gurmukhi: kVwk kr mukM auDM ] sVwk sYhQI juDM ]
transliteration: Kadaak Kar Moukan Udhan|| Sadaak Saihathoo Judhan||
translation: The sounds of working bows and striking daggers are being heard.

gurmukhi: ibAMq bwix brKXM ] ibsyK bIr prKXM ]18]174]
transliteration: Biant Baan(i) Barkhayan|| Bisekh Boor Parkhayan||18||174||
translation: In this continuous shower of arrows the significantly honoured heroes have been tasted.18.174.

gurmukhi: kVw kVI kiRpwxXM ] jtw jutI juAwxXM ]
transliteration: Kadaa Kadoo Kridaanayan|| Jataa Joutoo Juaanayan||
translation: Alongwith the clattering of swords, the daggers are striking fastly.

gurmukhi: su bIr jwgVdM jgy ] lVwk lwgVdM pgy ]19]175]
transliteration: Su Boor Jagaddan Jage|| Ladaak Laagaddan Page||19||175||
translation: The heroic warriors have been inspired to face the fighters. 19.175.

gurmukhi: JmI qyg J`tM ] CurI iCpR Cu`tM ]
translation: The striking swords are glistening and the daggers are striking fastly.
